Constant Properties

Zelix KlassMaster lets you change a constant's value. Press to make the change or press to undo a change.

Warning

Zelix KlassMaster performs no checking to ensure that changes you make to a constant's value make sense. In particular, it does no type checking. It is your responsibilty.
